00:04:13.320 --> 00:04:16.830
for space on the plate, it was
actually killing the bacteria

00:04:16.830 --> 00:04:18.380
that surrounded it on the plate.

00:04:18.380 --> 00:04:22.210
And from there, he recognized,
that insight that hmm,

00:04:22.210 --> 00:04:25.190
this could be a new question to study

00:04:25.190 --> 00:04:26.460
as opposed to the question

00:04:26.460 --> 00:04:29.000
